1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,440
各位弟兄姊妹早晨

2
00:00:01,440 --> 00:00:03,240
Good morning, brothers and sisters

3
00:00:03,240 --> 00:00:04,480
首先再一次

4
00:00:04,480 --> 00:00:06,320
恭祝各位父親節快樂

5
00:00:06,320 --> 00:00:08,480
Once again, Happy Father's Day

6
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:10,120
我們開始在港島之先

7
00:00:10,120 --> 00:00:11,480
我們同心低頭祈禱

8
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:13,000
Let's pray

9
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,560
莊主,我們感謝你

10
00:00:14,560 --> 00:00:16,000
Father, we give you thanks

11
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:17,840
你就是父親最好的榜樣

12
00:00:17,840 --> 00:00:19,440
Because you are the greatest example

13
00:00:19,440 --> 00:00:21,120
of being a good father

14
00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:22,040
我們又感謝你

15
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:23,440
讓我們有地上的父親

16
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:26,040
And we thank you for giving us earthly fathers

17
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:27,880
讓我們能夠在主你的裡面

18
00:00:27,880 --> 00:00:29,160
走在主你的愛中

19
00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:33,000
So that we can all walk in your truth and love

20
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:34,240
求主,你幫助我們

21
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:36,600
現在打開你的話語的時候

22
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:38,760
Father, as we open your word

23
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:40,160
求你開啟我們的心

24
00:00:40,160 --> 00:00:41,640
May you open our hearts

25
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:43,920
讓你的靈是充滿我們

26
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:45,640
May your spirit fill our hearts

27
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:47,040
向我們每一個人說話

28
00:00:47,040 --> 00:00:49,160
May you speak to each one of us

29
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:50,720
祈禱奉教主耶穌的名求

30
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:52,560
We pray all these things in Jesus' name

31
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:53,560
Amen

32
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:58,800
當想到父親節的信息的時候

33
00:00:58,800 --> 00:00:59,840
我就在想

34
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:03,360
So when I was pondering on the Father's Day message

35
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:04,560
I was thinking

36
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:06,800
其實我們每一個父母

37
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:09,840
我想我們都會有對子女的期盼

38
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,760
以及一個心腸

39
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:13,160
And I'm sure as parents

40
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:17,320
We have expectations and sentiments for our children

41
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:18,160
我相信你會覺得

42
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:20,240
哎呀,小孩生出來

43
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:21,960
你希望他快高長大

44
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:23,280
Or maybe you look at your children

45
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:25,400
and say, "Oh, I want you to grow healthy"

46
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:27,960
你不會想他經常都是這樣的高度

47
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:29,840
Of course you don't want them to be

48
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,720
