49
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:33,720
我記得曾經我和駱瑞很擔心

50
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:35,280
我第二的兒子

51
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:37,320
為什麼很遲都不說話

52
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:38,880
And at one point, my wife and I

53
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:40,680
were actually worried about our second son

54
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:44,200
because it took him a long time to speak

55
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,960
又或者你對子女的期望

56
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:47,560
他有好的嗜好

57
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:50,320
有健康的體魄

58
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:52,200
Maybe your expectation for your children

59
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:55,960
is healthy and also good hobbies

60
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:58,320
我想你也很想陪伴他們

61
00:01:58,320 --> 00:01:59,760
當你長大

62
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:02,600
當你自己年紀老了的時候

63
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,920
你也希望他們陪伴你

64
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,640
Or maybe you are thinking that

65
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,680
Oh, I want to be with them forever

66
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:12,000
so that they can also be with us forever

67
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:12,720
但無論如何

68
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:14,200
我想最重要的是

69
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:16,600
學業高升

70
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:17,360
事業高升

71
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:20,480
找到一個好的配偶

72
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:22,000
Maybe one of the most important things

73
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,880
is you want them to succeed

74
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:26,520
and to find a great spouse

75
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,520
當說到父親

76
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:30,280
我就一定想起我自己的父親

77
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,440
And talking about fathers

78
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:33,760
and of course, I thought of my own father

79
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:36,840
十年前在他的安息禮拜裡

80
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:39,160
At his memorial service ten years ago

81
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:42,360
我們一班兒孫唱了一首歌

82
