Our children and grandchildren

83
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:45,560
we sang a song

84
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,720
叫做《You Raise Me Up》

85
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,200
It's called《You Raise Me Up》

86
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:50,000
我想在中央大學很多人都認識的

87
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,400
If you know, you can sing along

88
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,520
我特別邀請了我們的家人

89
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:58,160
